{"word":"συναναγκάζω","slug":"συναναγκάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συναναγκάζω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>σω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to join</i> or <i>assist in compelling</i>, <b><a href='S:Isocrates'>Isocr.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be compelled at the same time</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to execute by force also</i>, <b><a href='S:Isocrates'>Isocr.</a></b>:— <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>ὅρκοι συνηναγκασμένοι</el> <i>extorted</i> oaths, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}